{"tid":1254431,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"嚴重懷疑稅務現場好撚多便衣狗！！！","createTime":"2019-06-24T06:26:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T10:29:44.000Z","uid":218595,"like":71,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"dfa171e7cf796c5df3d84de74bb82d9c2bdd9390","tid":1254431,"uid":218595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T06:26:42.000Z","msg":"大家小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n發夢去左現場，門口氣氛好撚鬼<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tbf9T0n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTbf9T0n.jpg&h=ca517753&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n圖中紫毛一黎就話自己係黎交税<br />\n大大聲話擾民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n吸引左一堆人去同佢講道理<br />\n之後就大叫你哋唔代表香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後有個啊嬸話要翻去翻工<br />\n現場有人話收曬工<br />\n但都俾佢入<br />\n講講下個紫毛就話啲人做咩查袋<br />\n直接大叫<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> <strong> 警察都冇權查袋 </strong> </span><br />\n<br />\n然後就話你哋都冇權查袋<br />\n心諗都冇人話要查袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後繼續叫囂<br />\n佢叫左唔夠五分鐘就行開左俾人訪問<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AtDrWdN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAtDrWdN.jpg&h=003e4eb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現場見佢做左至少兩個訪問<br />\n內容大致係話影響民生<br />\n你哋唔代表香港人果啲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/55zuT0N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F55zuT0N.jpg&h=834c6126&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n完曬之後覺得件事好撚鬼<br />\n<br />\n正常今日見幾個啊伯都係keep住屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但佢嘅屌，係有目的咁屌！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌完即走，正常啊伯都會走住黎屌<br />\n但佢唔係<br />\n佢快速行左去差佬果邊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wWrX2Un.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwWrX2Un.jpg&h=354b5bcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後我吊撚住佢尾黎影<br />\n佢行得好撚快咁去差佬度<br />\n本身佢停低左同差佬講兩句<br />\n但個白衫一望到我影佢<br />\n佢哋口噏噏之後紫衫即走<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vtdLsk8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvtdLsk8.jpg&h=5f38ef4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我見俾人發現左我都即刻走先<br />\n屌，最尾俾個啊伯阻住左個鏡頭<br />\n<br />\n現場好多中學生，冇乜經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總之<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>萬事小心！！！</strong></span>"},{"pid":"2171ade1441a130d7d8a197b61d2f26ec4e78b55","tid":1254431,"uid":50998,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T06:28:39.000Z","msg":"重要資料"},{"pid":"3ff724e8f56733d924b23e0c6785eb0a7728c822","tid":1254431,"uid":218595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T06:30:06.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家小心！"},{"pid":"45abc90b8d3a27650b3df3d0ee1120eb85529e91","tid":1254431,"uid":28510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T06:39:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d4c89611c32b2656c3de7d869c82b71a43ba7ac4","tid":1254431,"uid":42350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T06:40:44.000Z","msg":"差佬都有鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"532f189643597f30d1d54d799787aea8d5733db7","tid":1254431,"uid":32899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T06:42:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ad10db89a22059e1033c61f841c6b9f9f248242","tid":1254431,"uid":258098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dfa171e7cf796c5df3d84de74bb82d9c2bdd9390","tid":1254431,"uid":218595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"re